[
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "chapter"
    },
    "innerText": "(9) 4. Sativaggo"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "1-2. Satisampajaññasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "81-82"
      },
      ". Navamassa paṭhamaṃ heṭṭhā vuttanayameva. Dutiye ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "saddho"
      },
      "ti duvidhāya saddhāya samannāgato. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "No cupasaṅkamitā"
      },
      "ti na upaṭṭhahati. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "No"
      },
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ca paripucchitā"
      },
      "ti atthānatthaṃ kāraṇākāraṇaṃ paripucchitā na hoti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Samannāgato"
      },
      "ti ",
      " sāmiatthe paccattaṃ, samannāgatassāti vuttaṃ hoti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ekantapaṭibhānā tathāgataṃ dhammadesanā hotī"
      },
      "ti tathāgatassa ekantapaṭibhānā dhammadesanā hoti, ekanteneva paṭibhāti upaṭṭhātīti attho."
    ],
    "innerText": "81-82. Navamassa paṭhamaṃ heṭṭhā vuttanayameva. Dutiye saddhoti duvidhāya saddhāya samannāgato. No cupasaṅkamitāti na upaṭṭhahati. Noca paripucchitāti atthānatthaṃ kāraṇākāraṇaṃ paripucchitā na hoti. Samannāgatoti sāmiatthe paccattaṃ, samannāgatassāti vuttaṃ hoti. Ekantapaṭibhānā tathāgataṃ dhammadesanā hotīti tathāgatassa ekantapaṭibhānā dhammadesanā hoti, ekanteneva paṭibhāti upaṭṭhātīti attho."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "3. Mūlakasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "83"
      },
      ". Tatiye ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "sabbe dhammā"
      },
      "ti pañcakkhandhā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Chandamūlakā"
      },
      "ti ajjhāsayacchando kattukamyatāchando taṃ mūlaṃ etesanti chandamūlakā. Manasikārato sambhavantīti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "manasikārasambhavā"
      },
      ". Phassato samudenti rāsī bhavantīti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "phassasamudayā"
      },
      ". Vedanāya samosarantīti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "vedanāsamosaraṇā"
      },
      ". Samādhi etesaṃ pamukhoti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "samādhippamukhā"
      },
      ". Jeṭṭhakaṭṭhena sati adhipati etesanti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "satādhipateyyā,"
      },
      " satijeṭṭhakāti attho. Paññā uttarā etesanti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "paññuttarā"
      },
      ". Vimutti eva sāro etesanti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "vimuttisārā"
      },
      ". Ettha ca chandamūlakādayo cattāropi lokiyā kathitā, sesā lokiyalokuttaramissakāti."
    ],
    "innerText": "83. Tatiye sabbe dhammāti pañcakkhandhā. Chandamūlakāti ajjhāsayacchando kattukamyatāchando taṃ mūlaṃ etesanti chandamūlakā. Manasikārato sambhavantīti manasikārasambhavā. Phassato samudenti rāsī bhavantīti phassasamudayā. Vedanāya samosarantīti vedanāsamosaraṇā. Samādhi etesaṃ pamukhoti samādhippamukhā. Jeṭṭhakaṭṭhena sati adhipati etesanti satādhipateyyā, satijeṭṭhakāti attho. Paññā uttarā etesanti paññuttarā. Vimutti eva sāro etesanti vimuttisārā. Ettha ca chandamūlakādayo cattāropi lokiyā kathitā, sesā lokiyalokuttaramissakāti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "4. Corasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "84"
      },
      ". Catutthe ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "mahācoro"
      },
      "ti rajjantare dubbhituṃ samattho mahācoro. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Pariyāpajjatī"
      },
      "ti pariyādānaṃ gacchati. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Na ciraṭṭhitiko hotī"
      },
      "ti addhānaṃ pālento ṭhātuṃ na sakkoti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Appaharantassa paharatī"
      },
      "ti attano averine appaharante guṇasampanne ca mahallake ca taruṇadārake ca appaharitabbayuttake paharati. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Anavasesaṃ ādiyatī"
      },
      "ti nissesaṃ gaṇhāti. Byattacorānañhi idaṃ vattaṃ – parassa dvīsu sāṭakesu eko gahetabbo, ekasmiṃ sante dubbalaṃ datvā thiro gahetabbo. Puṭabhattataṇḍulādīsu ekaṃ koṭṭhāsaṃ datvā eko gahetabboti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Accāsanne kammaṃ karotī"
      },
      "ti gāmanigamarājadhānīnaṃ āsannaṭṭhāne corikakammaṃ karoti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Na ca nidhānakusalo hotī"
      },
      "ti yaṃ laddhaṃ, taṃ dakkhiṇeyye nidahituṃ cheko na hoti, paralokamaggaṃ na sodheti."
    ],
    "innerText": "84. Catutthe mahācoroti rajjantare dubbhituṃ samattho mahācoro. Pariyāpajjatīti pariyādānaṃ gacchati. Na ciraṭṭhitiko hotīti addhānaṃ pālento ṭhātuṃ na sakkoti. Appaharantassa paharatīti attano averine appaharante guṇasampanne ca mahallake ca taruṇadārake ca appaharitabbayuttake paharati. Anavasesaṃ ādiyatīti nissesaṃ gaṇhāti. Byattacorānañhi idaṃ vattaṃ – parassa dvīsu sāṭakesu eko gahetabbo, ekasmiṃ sante dubbalaṃ datvā thiro gahetabbo. Puṭabhattataṇḍulādīsu ekaṃ koṭṭhāsaṃ datvā eko gahetabboti. Accāsanne kammaṃ karotīti gāmanigamarājadhānīnaṃ āsannaṭṭhāne corikakammaṃ karoti. Na ca nidhānakusalo hotīti yaṃ laddhaṃ, taṃ dakkhiṇeyye nidahituṃ cheko na hoti, paralokamaggaṃ na sodheti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "5. Samaṇasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "85"
      },
      ". Pañcame ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "yaṃ samaṇenā"
      },
      "ti yaṃ guṇajātaṃ samaṇena pattabbaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vusīmatā"
      },
      "ti brahmacariyavāsaṃvutena. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Mutto mocemi bandhanā"
      },
      "ti ahaṃ sabbabandhanehi mutto hutvā mahājanampi rāgādibandhanato mocemi. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Paramadanto"
      },
      "ti aññena kenaci asikkhāpito acodito sayambhuñāṇena paṭivijjhitvā paramadamathena dantattā paramadanto nāma. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Parinibbuto"
      },
      "ti kilesaparinibbānena parinibbuto."
    ],
    "innerText": "85. Pañcame yaṃ samaṇenāti yaṃ guṇajātaṃ samaṇena pattabbaṃ. Vusīmatāti brahmacariyavāsaṃvutena. Mutto mocemi bandhanāti ahaṃ sabbabandhanehi mutto hutvā mahājanampi rāgādibandhanato mocemi. Paramadantoti aññena kenaci asikkhāpito acodito sayambhuñāṇena paṭivijjhitvā paramadamathena dantattā paramadanto nāma. Parinibbutoti kilesaparinibbānena parinibbuto."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "6. Yasasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "86"
      },
      ". Chaṭṭhe ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "mā ca mayā yaso"
      },
      "ti yaso ca mayā saddhiṃ mā gañchi. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Akasiralābhī"
      },
      "ti vipulalābhī. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sīlapaññāṇa"
      },
      "nti sīlañceva ñāṇañca. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Saṅgammā"
      },
      "ti sannipatitvā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Samāgammā"
      },
      "ti samāgantvā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Saṅgaṇikavihāra"
      },
      "nti gaṇasaṅgaṇikavihāraṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Na hi nūname"
      },
      "ti na hi nūna ime. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tathā hi paname"
      },
      "ti tathā hi pana ime. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Aṅgulipatodakehī"
      },
      "ti aṅgulipatodayaṭṭhiṃ katvā vijjhanena. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sañjagghante"
      },
      "ti mahāhasitaṃ hasante. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Saṃkīḷante"
      },
      "ti keḷiṃ karonte."
    ],
    "innerText": "86. Chaṭṭhe mā ca mayā yasoti yaso ca mayā saddhiṃ mā gañchi. Akasiralābhīti vipulalābhī. Sīlapaññāṇanti sīlañceva ñāṇañca. Saṅgammāti sannipatitvā. Samāgammāti samāgantvā. Saṅgaṇikavihāranti gaṇasaṅgaṇikavihāraṃ. Na hi nūnameti na hi nūna ime. Tathā hi panameti tathā hi pana ime. Aṅgulipatodakehīti aṅgulipatodayaṭṭhiṃ katvā vijjhanena. Sañjagghanteti mahāhasitaṃ hasante. Saṃkīḷanteti keḷiṃ karonte."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "7. Pattanikujjanasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "87"
      },
      ". Sattame ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "nikkujjeyyā"
      },
      "ti tena dinnassa deyyadhammassa appaṭiggahaṇatthaṃ pattanikkujjanakammavācāya nikujjeyya, na adhomukhaṭhapanena. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Alābhāyā"
      },
      "ti ",
      " catunnaṃ paccayānaṃ alābhatthāya. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Anatthāyā"
      },
      "ti upaddavāya avaḍḍhiyā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ukkujjeyyā"
      },
      "ti ukkujjanakammavācāya ukkujjeyya."
    ],
    "innerText": "87. Sattame nikkujjeyyāti tena dinnassa deyyadhammassa appaṭiggahaṇatthaṃ pattanikkujjanakammavācāya nikujjeyya, na adhomukhaṭhapanena. Alābhāyāti catunnaṃ paccayānaṃ alābhatthāya. Anatthāyāti upaddavāya avaḍḍhiyā. Ukkujjeyyāti ukkujjanakammavācāya ukkujjeyya."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "8. Appasādapavedanīyasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "88"
      },
      ". Aṭṭhame ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "appasādaṃ pavedeyyu"
      },
      "nti appasannabhāvaṃ jānāpeyyuṃ. Appasādaṃ pavedentena pana kiṃ kātabbanti? Nisinnāsanato na uṭṭhātabbaṃ na vanditabbaṃ na paccuggamanaṃ kātabbaṃ, na deyyadhammo dātabbo. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Agocare"
      },
      "ti pañcavidhe agocare."
    ],
    "innerText": "88. Aṭṭhame appasādaṃ pavedeyyunti appasannabhāvaṃ jānāpeyyuṃ. Appasādaṃ pavedentena pana kiṃ kātabbanti? Nisinnāsanato na uṭṭhātabbaṃ na vanditabbaṃ na paccuggamanaṃ kātabbaṃ, na deyyadhammo dātabbo. Agocareti pañcavidhe agocare."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "9. Paṭisāraṇīyasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "89"
      },
      ". Navame ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "dhammikañca gihipaṭissava"
      },
      "nti ‘‘imaṃ temāsaṃ idheva vasitabba’’nti vutto ‘‘evaṃ hotū’’tiādinā nayena paṭissavaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Na saccāpetī"
      },
      "ti vuttaṃ na saccaṃ karoti visaṃvādeti."
    ],
    "innerText": "89. Navame dhammikañca gihipaṭissavanti ‘‘imaṃ temāsaṃ idheva vasitabba’’nti vutto ‘‘evaṃ hotū’’tiādinā nayena paṭissavaṃ. Na saccāpetīti vuttaṃ na saccaṃ karoti visaṃvādeti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "10. Sammāvattanasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "90"
      },
      ". Dasame ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "paccekaṭṭhāne"
      },
      "ti adhipatiṭṭhāne jeṭṭhakaṭṭhāne. Tañhi jeṭṭhakaṃ katvā kiñci saṅghakammaṃ kātuṃ na labhati. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Na ca tena mūlena vuṭṭhāpetabbo"
      },
      "ti taṃ mūlaṃ katvā abbhānakammaṃ kātuṃ na labhati. Sesaṃ sabbattha uttānamevāti."
    ],
